Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the mail delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a wonderful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're new here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Cozy Glow, Professor\NSparkle's Friendship Assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first class is\Njust down that hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.55,0:00:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A seven-letter\Nword for teamwork...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tried\Nsynergy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Cozy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. What are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning,\NProfessor Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The mail's here already?\NWhat time is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late for my class's\Nfield trip to Cloudsdale!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Professor Rainbow\NDash to cover for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said.. yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh! I told her\Nhow busy you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much her\Nloyalty meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I also color-coded your teaching\Nschedule by friendship element,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and cataloged all the magical\Nartifacts in the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that's OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,OK? Cozy,\Nthat's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like my\Nright-hoof pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\NI'd do without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggle]\NIt's like you taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping is what\Nfriendship's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And hopefully my class\Nis learning that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,on their field\Ntrip right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they might do\Nsome sight-seeing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pegasus Weather Factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Every drop of rain or flake of\Nsnow from Cloudsdale
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,comes from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Whoaaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! The cool\Nstuff's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I've never stood on\Na cloud before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, normally.\NBut for our trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast a spell that lets\Nus walk like Pegasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come check out this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're too scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,AHHH! NOW YONA SCARED!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! We gotta catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Yona!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You like flying, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying. Not falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's like my spell\Nstopped working!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's.. never happened before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The students dropped\Nout of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down.\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast a spell for our\Nfield trip to Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But my magic just.. failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We barely caught\Neverypony in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it's nothing\Nto worry about, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you did your\Nspell wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't drop that book...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you did\Nyour spell wrong..?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity: OWWWW!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity ran into the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic is GONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had to use my\Nhooves to coif my tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still think there's\Nnothing to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic can't just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something has to\Nbe causing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we learn in class about\Na creature that eats magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tir...T..Tur..something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Tirek!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he trapped in Tartarus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!? What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had a letter\Nget stuck before..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Princess Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all been called to an\Nemergency meeting in Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure I know\Nwhat it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: Throughout our city,\Nponies have been reporting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,tales of their magic failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Spells going wrong,\Npotions not working...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even raising the moon\Nhas become difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there similar\Ntroubles in Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We experienced it first hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same in my kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart\Nseems safe for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but.. I worry if this continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Letter for the Princesses,\Nfrom Starswirl the Bearded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It is even more\Nterrible than we feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is disappearing\Nall across Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl believes the power\Nwill drain from our land
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,First, unicorn magic\Nand spells will fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's happening now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,On the second day, creatures\Nwill lose their magic abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, magical\Nartifacts will stop working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When the sun sets\Non the third day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the magic in our\Nworld will be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is this happening now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the worst part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anypony checked on Tirek?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the big red scary\Ncentaur who eats magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would we want...\NOhhhh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If he has found some way\Nto escape his prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or work from within it, he\Ncould be responsible for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the best\Nexplanation so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony should\Ninvestigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no no no no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not without us you wo--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Did you say "we"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally learned\Nthat it's OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to count on your\Nfriends for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...You do want\Nto come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, DUH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We will search for ways\Nto protect Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in your absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. Tartarus has\Nchanged since you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It now holds many\Ndangerous creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and you won't be able\Nto rely on your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With her friends by her\Nside, she won't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I left you my lesson\Nplan, all my student files,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and my annotated syllabus notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything goes\Nwrong, get Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should just\Nclose the school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and send my students home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Would you go save\NEquestria already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Cozy packed us all up for a\Ntrip to bad guy central.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget\Nthe sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I marked whose is\Nwhose just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight can't\Nstand mustard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet\Nof you, Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But Twilight has asked me to\Nstay here to run the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I thought that after what\Nhappened last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you survive\NDiscord,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,anything else is\Na piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus she'll have\Nyou to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll be the\Nbest assistant ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! We can start\Nworking on your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,substitute Headmare plans\Nright now, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...! Uh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Nothing to\Nworry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me there's\Nnothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning,\Nfriendship students!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're all sad\NProfessor Sparkle is away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, because\Nshe left ME in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to do things just\Nthe way she would!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. I thought Starlight Glimmer was\Ngonna be temporary headmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She was. But she\Nleft me this note:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have to go. Twilight\Nneeds my help."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"I know the school is in\Ngood hooves with you, Cozy."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let Starlight\Ndown, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just kinda weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like... why'd she\Nchange her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Starlight\Nwrite a note,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of say goodbye\Nto us herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Smolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You forget; we're\Nnot scheming dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like somecreature\Nneeds to do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a little extra\Nfriendship homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak not pony either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If Smolder get homework,\NYona get homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Homework party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What loyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Rainbow Dash\Nwould be so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You all are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm grateful\Nbecause it will be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,awfully hard running a\Nwhole school alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I count on each\Nof you to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like our\Nprofessors taught us:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,together, we can get\Nthrough anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[thunk]\NOwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I have had it with\Nthese horrible flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[whining] I miss my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tried using your\Ntail to shoo them away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Bite your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for decorative\Npurposes only.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I didn't know we\Npacked green cupcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. We didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have gone bad without\Nmagic to keep them cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic this, magic that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need magic to\Ngo on a little hike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to think more\Nlike Earth ponies, y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny's Apple Core\NNo Bite No More.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll keep the flies off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniff] Ooh, it smells\Njust like it looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if our\Nfood's spoiled,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,these blueberries are\Nstill good to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad we can't do anything\Nabout the rainstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop that storm by\Nmyself but I can still help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have all the\Nmagic we need right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I don't\Nwant to get it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow baked our\Nclass cupcakes today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And she made all of us\Nfriendship bracelets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the nicest\Npony I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm SO glad\Nshe's Headmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, temporary\NHeadmare, right guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh. Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Twilight takes her time\Ncoming back, I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally! We thought you\Nforgot about study club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow gave our class tickets\Nto a Sapphire Shores concert
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in Ponyville tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the feeling\NCozy's trying too hard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to make us like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she just\Nwants to help us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,keep our minds off of how scary\Nit is that magic's disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she up to behind those\Nbig eyes and bouncy curls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And why Cozy Pony coming out\Ncatacombs so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only\Ndoor to Tartarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The good news is, the\Nseal isn't broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so we know Tirek\Ndidn't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya got bad news too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I was here, I had\Nto use magic to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And according to Starswirl,\Nall unicorn magic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,was gone by yesterday's sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Free pizza delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Always worked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did any of y'all pack something\Nthat could actually help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,These all do magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but not the kind we're\Nlooking for, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Key of Unfettered Entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you find this, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow must have\Npacked it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She really did\Nthink of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what does it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It can magically open any door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And since artifacts like this\Nhaven't lost their power yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it only works once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockatrice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll turn you to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless it's really\Nbouncy stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he lost\Nhis magic too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All the creatures\Nhere must have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl said that would\Nhappen on the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it should\Nmake me feel safer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it just makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta fix this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly! She's\Naway on a quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching the\Nschool for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is failing\Nacross our land,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and she left a {\i1}foal{\i0}\Nin charge of this facility!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything\NI can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's folly stops here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, {\i1}I{\i0} am Headstallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have quite a\Nfew changes to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If all these monsters\Nlost their magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then getting past Cerberus\Nshould be easy-peasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]\NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me, puppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a very good guard dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But um, we were wondering if we\Ncould get by to check on Tirek?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a\Ntowel, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess of Friendship,\Nhere for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done to earn\Nthe honor of your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We want answers, Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is disappearing\Nfrom Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of such\N[slurp] delicious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had all that magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think I'd still\Nbe locked up in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I might know\Nsomething about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Twilight's\Nstudent files!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,These aren't. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With Equestria under attack,\Nponies must stand together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight has endangered us all\Nby skipping off on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"friendship trips," while these\Ndangerous creatures run loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think {\i1}they're{\i0} the\Nreason magic is disappearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,do you?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to warn Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But since she is gone, it falls\Nto me to protect you foals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,from those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's blaming us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like it\Ncame from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You again, as I suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, this\Nschool is {\i1}pony only.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As nature intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you refuse to explain\Nyour plot against Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and return the magic\Nyou stole,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you will stay here while I\Nsummon your guardians
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right about them from\Nthe beginning, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you saying!?\N-Sandbar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything\Nto do with creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that could threaten Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wisely put, colt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony will come to\Ntheir senses, ...eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I ran\Nout of apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the Cutie Mark Crusaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Neighsay\Nlocked them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought Cozy\NGlow was in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys are good buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can convince her\Nto distract Neighsay,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can break out my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do mulberries\Nhave seeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Equestria's\Nmagic going, Tirek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's making it disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let me out, I'm sure\Nit would jog my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say? I scratch\Nyour back, you scratch mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout you tell\Nus what you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or you'll be stuck\Nhere forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're out of magic keys\Nand nopony can open the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, dear. I hadn't\Nthought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just as\Ntrapped as Tirek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet revenge for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems my little protégé's\Nplan worked after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Which little protégé?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pen pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Each letter had so many\Nquestions about draining magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you answered them!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I simply pointed my pen\Npal in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just tell us\Nyour pen pal's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, since we're\Nstuck here anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The irony is too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I could've sworn I saw\Nher come down this way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when she left her office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoying yourself\Nin there, Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I had to push you\Nin, but what else could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to\Nruin all my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You might get some company soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can't make that\Nannoying Neighsay BACK OFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All this magic needs time to\Ndrain from Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before my vortex sucks\Nit to another realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days can sure\Nseem like forever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you ponies\Ngot it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship isn't {\i1}magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship is POWER!
